query:
SELECT DATE(c.consumptionDate) as date, p.name as product, c.quantity 
FROM consumption c 
JOIN products p ON c.productId = p.id 
ORDER BY c.consumptionDate, p.name 
INTO OUTFILE '/tmp/db_consumption.csv' 
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ',' 
ENCLOSED BY '"' 
LINES TERMINATED BY '\n';
